messages.msgSnippet: Hi to all! Just wanted to tell everyone I got the puter fixed. YEAH! We had to wipe out the hard drive and install a new one. Then the printer went AWOL, so I
messages.messageBody:
Hi to all! Just wanted to tell everyone I got the puter fixed. YEAH! We had
to wipe out the hard drive and install a new one. Then the printer went AWOL,
so I went to Darin's store and picked up a new one today. But here I am... <g>
I took one look at my mailbox and just deleted, so forgive me if I jump in
somewhere. I am just thrilled to be able to get online, visit websites, and
work on the puter again! I lost all my favorite places, all my saved files,
all my diary... I couldn't back anything up, it was horrible. (insert pity
here. <g>)
~Nancy~ who is thrilled to be back! Can you tell? :o)
